quran[53]{c,v,t}:
  51,31,"UIbrâhîm wathi: “Myalezo mni na (lo) nize ngawo (apha) kanye kanye nina ziThunywa?”"
  51,32,"Zathi zona: “Inene thina sithunyelwe kubantu abazizaphula- mthetho"
  51,33,Ukuba sithulule phezu kwabo amatye odongwe
  51,34,Aphawulelwe abagabadeli phambi kweNkosi yakho.”
  51,35,Ngoko ke Sakhupha (wonke) olikholwa phakathi apho
  51,36,Kananjalo aSizanga Sifumane mntu ngaphandle komzi omnye wamaMuslim (umzi kaLût neentombi zakhe)
  51,37,Sashiya umqondiso apho kwabo basoyikayo isohlwayo esibuhlungu
  51,38,"Kananjalo kuMûsâ (kwakukho umnqondiso), ukumthumela kweThu kuFir’awn negunya elicacileyo"
  51,39,"Kodwa (uFir’awn) watshikila nabalandeli bakhe, wathi: “(UMûsâ) ngumenzi wemilingo nephambana.”"
  51,40,Samntywilisela elwandle yena namadoda omkhosi wakhe ngenxa yokuba wayesoleka
  51,41,"Nakuma’Ad (wabakhona umnqondiso), xa Sathumela umoya oludlolo1 (owavuthuzayo ngokuchaseneyo nabo)"
  51,42,"Awuzanga usindise nenye into owawubhudla phezu kwayo koko wayishiya itshabalele, ibubutyobo"
  51,43,"NakwaThamûd, xa kwathiwa kubo: “Yibani nizonwabisa okwethutyana.”"
  51,44,"Bona baba nendelelo ngokubhekiselele kumyalelo weNkosi yabo, ngoko iindudumo zabahlasela besajongile"
  51,45,"Azanga bakwazi ukuvuka ke, bengazanga bakwazi nokuzikhusela"
  51,46,"Kananjalo Satshabalalisa abantu bakwaNûh ngaphambili, inene, bona babengabantu, abagabadelayo"
  51,47,"Thina Sawabumba amazulu ngamandla. Inene, Thina Siyakwazi ukwandisa ukwandlaleka kwephakade"
  51,48,"Nomhlaba Siwandlalile, Hayi ubuncutshe boMlungiseleli (wendalo)"
  51,49,Kwizinto zonke Sidale amaqabane (azo) ngambini khona ukuze nikhumbule (iziBele zika-Allâh)
  51,50,Balekelani kuAllâh ke ngoko. Inene mna ndinguMlumkisi kuni ocacileyo
  51,51,Musani ukwayamanisa thixo wumbi kuAllâh. Inene mna ndinguMlumkisi ocacileyo kuni
  51,52,"Kwangokunjalo akuzanga khe kufike nawuphi na uMthunywa kwabangaphambili kunabo bangathi: “Umenzi wemilingo okanye iphambana.”"
  51,53,Ingaba babecetyiswe ngabo2 ukuba benze le nto? Nakanye bona buqu bangabantu abagabadela batsiba imida (ekungakholweni)
  51,54,Bayeke ke wena (Muhammad) kuba akuyi kusoleka. (njengoko uwuvakalisile umyalezo kubo)
  51,55,"Bakhumbuze kananjalo, kuba inene inkumbuzo ilulutho kumakholwa"
  51,56,Kananjalo aNdidalanga abantu neeJinni ngaphandle (kokubadalela) ukuba banqule Mna
  51,57,"Andinasixhaso Ndisifunayo kubo, Ndingafuni nakondliwa ngabo Mna"
  51,58,"Inene nguAllâh OnguMondli, uMninimandla amakhulu"
  51,59,Ke kaloku inene okwabo benza ubugwenxa sisabelo (sesohlwayo)esinjengesabelosabahlobobabo(abalandulelayo eli). MabangaNdiqhwayi ngokungenamonde ke
  51,60,Yeha ke kwabo bangakholwayo kwiMini abathenjiswe ngayo
  52,1,(Ndifunga ngeNtaba) yeTûr
  52,2,NangeNcwadi ebhaliweyo
  52,3,Kumacwecwe avulwe ondlalwa
  52,4,NangoMzi1 ohanjelwa rhoqo
  52,5,Nangophahla (izulu) oluphakamele phezulu
  52,6,Nangolwandle oluzele (ngumlilo)
  52,7,Inene isohlwayo seNkosi yakho siza kwenzeka
  52,8,Ngokuba akukho mthinteli (waso)
  52,9,NgeMini izulu liya kuzamazama ngokujikelezayo
  52,10,Neentaba zigqithe zimke
  52,11,Yeha ke ngalooMini kubaphiki
  52,12,Abancokola amampunge bezonwabisa
  52,13,Ngemini abaya kutshovelwa eMlilweni wesiHogo ngamandla
  52,14,"(Kuya kuthiwa kubo): “Nangu ke lo Mlilo naniwuphika"
  52,15,"Ngumlingo na lo, okanye aniboni"
  52,16,(Ngenani ke) nitshe phakathi apho; yibani nomonde okanye ningabi namonde kuyafana kuni. Nihlawulwa ngoko nakwenzayo kuphela
  52,17,Inene amalungisa aya kuba semiyezweni naselonwabeni
  52,18,"Esonwabela oko iNkosi yawo Iwanike kona, Ibe neNkosi yawo Iwakhusele esohlwayweni soMlilo wesiHogo"
  52,19,"(Kuya kuthiwa kwabakholwayo): “Yidlani, nisele, naneliseke ngenxa yoko nakwenzayo.”"
  52,20,"Baya kuba bengqiyamile ezitroneni ezidwelisiweyo, kananjalo Siya kubatshatisa neembelukazi zabafazi abanamehlo amakhulu (amahle)"
  52,21,"Abo baya bakholwa abantwana babo balandela ekhondweni labo ngokholo Siya kubadibanisa nenzala yabo, kwaye aSiyi kubabandeza nto kwizinto zabo. Umntu ngamnye awakusebenzelayo kugciniwe"
  52,22,Kananjalo Siya kubapha iziqhamo nenyama nantoni na abaya kuyinqwenela
  52,23,Baya kunikana indebe (yewayini) apho akuyi kubakho ntetho imbi nakwenziwa kwasono